{"tid":2237170,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"近千黃店周末舉行「10.10全民感謝日」；黃洋達：黃色經濟圈會真正傷害香港根基；陳雲：黃色經濟圈是歧視，無家教、無品。","createTime":"2020-10-10T04:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T05:51:44.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"35ee1784559405ca98e5573a43e62759dd0f6689","tid":2237170,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/KWL4HQQOQRHMRB7T3Z4GXX57DU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FKWL4HQQOQRHMRB7T3Z4GXX57DU%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=58025a2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FKWL4HQQOQRHMRB7T3Z4GXX57DU%2F&h=3585a290\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/KWL4HQQOQRHMRB7T3Z4GXX57DU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XM0qGc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXM0qGc5.jpg&h=446dd730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃洋達：<br />\n其實對於黃色經濟圈，來自共匪的批評不多，主要的批評是來自熱狗和國師。<br />\n為什麼？ <br />\n因為我們真的關心香港，我們知道什麼事會真正傷害香港根基，我們半絕望地期許香港還有救，不願看見香港死於愚昧。<br />\n一心想要殖民換血的共匪，看見你們做自殘蠢事，只會旁觀冷笑。<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：黃色經濟圈的政治立場歧視。泛民支持者的德性，就是有風使盡𢃇、得勢不饒人，只要不是犯法的就做。香港的歧視條例，只是包括性別歧視、殘疾歧視、家庭崗位歧視及種族歧視，並未包括政治立場歧視。但並不是說，我們可以歧視政治立場，肆意批鬥，實行黃絲民主專政。不將政治歧視、宗教信仰歧視寫入法例，是因為無法公平 執行而已。<br />\n於是，就有基於政治立場歧視的黃色經濟圈成立，香港人七嘴八舌講起來，大家面不紅心不跳，竟然毫無羞恥之心！<br />\n香港人，確係好嘢。普世價值？贏選舉就得啦，仲講普世 價值。那些口講普世價值的人，原來無傳統道德觀念的，無家教、做人無品。<br />\n（我今日在網台說，很多人不會因為共產黨而移民，但會 因為黃絲而移民。）"},{"pid":"b197a15b214951d1907fb26aa2d4d0e7b4578bd1","tid":2237170,"uid":273218,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"中共最驚反共本土建制派既成立<br />\n<br />\n其實唔需要好激<br />\n<br />\n香港人需要有自己經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n先能維持自主"},{"pid":"d877c2cc417aa27fb4b452cf6f9c9b7815fa8f63","tid":2237170,"uid":59639,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"支持黃店係最基本嘅事 <br />\n<br />\n希望大家真係抵制垃圾藍店唔好再食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n盡量去like 同幫襯黃店 <br />\n<br />\n呢個時勢肯表態嘅店鋪唔容易"},{"pid":"5ec7d5e4a41b4f2dde62901824e84dfae7a46906","tid":2237170,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"只要唔系部部電視機都長開播住既ＴＶＢ<br />\n<br />\n唔理乜店都可幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a043c571b9f7066d03881c3a0d03271464575210","tid":2237170,"uid":128594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"熱青城班垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d53f4be551ade9c4c09eb3460b73043d7efc4a0","tid":2237170,"uid":23993,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"望到樓主就知樓主連軍曹都未有得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c7e12b89a31643c1203e3ab8fa29a873e76484","tid":2237170,"uid":178382,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"好人經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4893da266fb833efa4f7f2147c2bb383f1a89fe","tid":2237170,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:38:36.000Z","msg":"呢兩條傻閪而家扮都費事扮"},{"pid":"3424f76cd824972398c15b87284d9c24162f1f73","tid":2237170,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"熱狗反對<br />\n證明又做啱喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32ed37ffd49c1aaeb38b5d3593c0cf6063918c4","tid":2237170,"uid":34424,"like":2,"dislike":0